OL,3,CWork begins on mural honouring music
OL,4,Clegend Mani
OL,6,FWork has begun on a mural celebrating
OL,7,Fthe life of music legend Gary 'Mani'
OL,8,FMounfield.
OL,10,FThe Stone Roses and Primal Scream
OL,11,Fbassist died at the age of 63 in
OL,12,FNovember 2025.
OL,14,FThe mural, supported by his brother
OL,15,FGreg Mounfield, was funded by a
OL,16,Fcrowdfunder, with all profits being
OL,17,Fgiven to cancer charity Maggie's ` a
OL,18,Fcharity close to Mani and his wife
OL,19,FImelda's hearts during her cancer
OL,20,Ftreatment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
