CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776445554
OL,3,CWork begins on mural honouring music
OL,4,Clegend Mani
OL,6,FThe project is organised by not-for-
OL,7,Fprofit art organisation GRIT Studios,
OL,8,Fwas inspired in part by Ian Brown's
OL,9,Fmoving eulogy at Manchester Cathedral.
OL,11,FIn his memorable tribute to his friend
OL,12,Fand band mate, he said: "I want to
OL,13,Fstart a campaign for a Mani statue `
OL,14,F50 feet high ` a solid gold statue!
OL,15,FMani forever! God Bless Mani!"
OL,17,FThe mural will be found on the wall at
OL,18,FLafadi's Pub on Oldham Road in
OL,19,FFailsworth, where Mani grew up.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
