FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776445554
OL,3,CWork begins on mural honouring music
OL,4,Clegend Mani
OL,6,FThe piece is being created artist
OL,7,FPic.One.Art, and is expected to take
OL,8,Faround a week to complete.
OL,10,FThey said: "I couldn't wait to get
OL,11,Fstarted on this mural. Mani meant so
OL,12,Fmuch to so many people, and it's an
OL,13,Fhonour to be asked to create something
OL,14,Fthat celebrates his life here in
OL,15,FFailsworth.
OL,17,F"There's a real sense of love behind
OL,18,Fthis project, and I'm excited to bring
OL,19,Fthat to the wall for everyone to see."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
