PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776445554
OL,3,CWork begins on mural honouring music
OL,4,Clegend Mani
OL,6,FMani's brother Greg worked with GRIT
OL,7,FStudios to organise the project and
OL,8,Fthe location.
OL,10,FJohn Macaulay, co-founder of GRIT
OL,11,FStudios said: "Mani was one of the
OL,12,Fwarmest, funniest and most generous
OL,13,Fpeople I've ever known. He had time
OL,14,Ffor everyone.
OL,16,F"The work we did together over a
OL,17,Fdecade ago genuinely changed my life,
OL,18,Fand without his support, GRIT Studios
OL,19,Fprobably wouldn't exist. The support
OL,20,Fso far for this campaign has been
OL,21,Fincredible.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
